{"tid":277632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港青泰國運毒案，其實係香港海關同泰國海關合謀陷害","createTime":"2017-06-09T18:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T23:15:56.000Z","uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a76e515ae26cb0cf5c2fb02c505ab34bba876aee","tid":277632,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:28:41.000Z","msg":"話咗係有情報通知香港海關，有人運毒去泰國， 其實一早準備犧牲三個港青，香港海關可以開單，泰國海關又可以收黑肥肥，其實當三個港青闖關被捕時，其他毒品已經大量地由其他人帶過關！<br />\n<br />\n一向係咁有效運作， 香港海關唔知害死過幾多香港人！"},{"pid":"454d14ffb236f6b5fa79cd0730f887b3a9e0702f","tid":277632,"uid":42379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"陷害？運毒就抵撚死，就算要打靶都係抵撚死嘅"},{"pid":"91a5f9fe89002bb9de96582df93486c9ddcafd3a","tid":277632,"uid":64582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"無帶我塞比你就叫陷害姐<br />\n你斷正係叫抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5f54fb083954dc2518c1948a8bdf1e21bf2d6c","tid":277632,"uid":65263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係黑警提供情報比泰國咩<br />\n關海關咩事"},{"pid":"a0e7c904ee73163bca29db3100f1f46b3541df98","tid":277632,"uid":23451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係黑警提供情報比泰國咩<br />\n關海關咩事</blockquote><br />\n毒販提供情報俾黑警<br />\n拉d細既<br />\n大既冇事<br />\n<br />\n世界不嬲係咁撚樣運作<br />\n冇人犧牲哪來成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d924695e83c1ff5ab99871a4a14210b7815ad7","tid":277632,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"但 d 毒品真係響佢扡行李度搜出黎喎<br />\n佢地又自認咗收 8000蚊幫人帶貨<br />\n咁都叫陷害？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0be3d4e40df2c3edd78b4433d97174e76306eb","tid":277632,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:13:33.000Z","msg":"據悉，今次行動是泰國海關於上周六接到香港警方的通報，稱近日將有香港毒販從巴西運毒入境泰國，再轉運到香港。海關遂聯同各部門合作，成功拘捕兩男一女毒販，分別為19歲的Fong Yee Ting、22歲的Tung Wing Yan及24歲的Yau Kit Long。3人其後供稱，他們受僱於一名叫「明姐」的香港人，給每人8000港元讓他們從巴西運毒到曼谷，原定在市中心一間酒店交接毒品。<br />\n<br />\n警方獲悉後迅速趕往酒店，但事先已被「明姐」搶先一步逃離出境返回香港，泰方正與香港警方聯合調查中。泰國海關廳長素琳表示，今次能一舉繳獲12.3公斤可卡因，是有關當局密切合作的成果，將繼續打擊國際間的販毒網絡。"},{"pid":"228620205e403647578b4ff24fadae2cb72aebfa","tid":277632,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係黑警提供情報比泰國咩<br />\n關海關咩事</blockquote><br />\n毒販提供情報俾黑警<br />\n拉d細既<br />\n大既冇事<br />\n<br />\n世界不嬲係咁撚樣運作<br />\n冇人犧牲哪來成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定要有甲 乙先生存到？ 好似唔係喎！<br />\n<br />\n細既有冇事 都有大既存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38edbe3bc5850e60f48394502895bb13c32df0f3","tid":277632,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e8368b9c3e824ec135de1c8916959fb6a7ecada","tid":277632,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"屈插贓嫁禍埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707f1613a795aa6a9fdbac43a6747ef2ca5d979a","tid":277632,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係黑警提供情報比泰國咩<br />\n關海關咩事</blockquote><br />\n毒販提供情報俾黑警<br />\n拉d細既<br />\n大既冇事<br />\n<br />\n世界不嬲係咁撚樣運作<br />\n冇人犧牲哪來成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世界從來只懲罰窮人蠢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe8d7ba5deec7b8325e8250accb31830e50dff5","tid":277632,"ui